CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 29, 1963, pg. 19, reads: "1963 Courier-WAMO Home-A-Rama Exhibitors who were not shown on last week's picture page are shown here... 2. Grand Prize Winner, Mrs. Fred Jones, happily accepts her prize, a Norge Gas Range, courtesy of The Natural Gas Companies, from Harold Mason... All Home-A-Rama Photos (Including last week's) by Charles (Teenie) Harris."
TitMainTitle: Grand prize winner Mrs. Fred Jones, and two men, including Harold Mason, posed next to oven with WAMO sign, on stage with Natural Gas Companies appliance display at 1963 Pittsburgh Courier - WAMO, Home-A-Rama fair, Syria Mosque
